{
  "key": 62487,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_YoureTheExpert",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh?\n",
        "Welcome!\r",
        "You saw the notice outside about\n",
        "us hiring, right?\r",
        "Is that a Pokédex there?\n",
        "Then you must know Professor Rowan!\r",
        "You’re just the Pokémon-searching\n",
        "expert we’ve been looking for!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_HeresYourAssignment",
      "en_US": [
        "Here you are!\n",
        "Good!\r",
        "We’ve got a deadline to meet.\n",
        "Here’s your assignment.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_BringMeThisPokemon",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 0, 0, 0}.\n",
        "I want you to bring me one.\r",
        "You must bring it today, or we’re not\n",
        "gonna be able to run our main article.\r",
        "I’ll pay you with a Heart Scale and some\n",
        "Poké Balls for it."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_DidYouBringUsThePokemon",
      "en_US": [
        "What’s up? Did you bring us\n",
        "the Pokémon we needed?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_ThatsItThanks",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh! Ohh! Ohhh!\n",
        "That’s it! {STRVAR_1 0, 0, 0}!\r",
        "Thanks!\n",
        "Let me get a closer look!\r",
        "...I see, hmhm...\n",
        "Right, right... That’s it!\r",
        "Thank you!\n",
        "I can write a great article now!\r",
        "This is for your trouble.\n",
        "It’s not much, but thanks!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_IHopeYoullHelpAgainTomorrow",
      "en_US": [
        "You really came through for us!\n",
        "I hope you’ll help us again tomorrow!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_YourBagIsStuffedFull",
      "en_US": [
        "Whoops! What’s all this?\n",
        "Your Bag is stuffed full.\r",
        "I’ll hold on to these until\n",
        "the next time."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_HeresYourReward",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh, there you are! Here’s your\n",
        "reward for the last assignment!\r",
        "It’s not much, but thanks!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_StillHaventCaughtThePokemon",
      "en_US": [
        "What’s wrong? You still haven’t\n",
        "caught the {STRVAR_1 0, 0, 0} we need?\r",
        "We’re counting on you to come through\n",
        "for us!\r",
        "I’ll pay you a Heart Scale and some\n",
        "Poké Balls for it, OK?\r",
        "Bring us the {STRVAR_1 0, 0, 0} before\n",
        "the date rolls over!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_FailedToBringThePokemon",
      "en_US": [
        "Now, now! You failed to bring me the\n",
        "Pokémon I asked for...\r",
        "Things like that can happen, but\n",
        "we need you to come up big for us!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_IllHaveAnotherAssignmentTomorrow",
      "en_US": [
        "OK! I’ll crank out a riveting story\n",
        "based on this!\r",
        "Oh, right! I’ll have another\n",
        "assignment for you tomorrow!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_TheNewspaperIsTiny",
      "en_US": [
        "The Sinnoh region’s newspaper is\n",
        "tiny, but it has many fans.\r",
        "That newspaper is printed right\n",
        "here!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_TopStory",
      "en_US": [
        "“Weekly Poké Ball Roundup”\n",
        "is the featured top story.\r",
        "It’s a feature article on new types\n",
        "of Poké Balls.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_ReadWhichArticle",
      "en_US": "Which article would you like to read?"
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_ArticleDuskBall",
      "en_US": [
        "Dark caves and streets unlit at\n",
        "night are forbidding places to go.\r",
        "If you’re threatened by the dark,\n",
        "a supply of Dusk Balls is your\f",
        "biggest ally!\r",
        "Use them in the dark for the best\n",
        "Pokémon-catching performance!\r",
        "Keep the dark at bay on your travels\n",
        "with Dusk Balls!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_ArticleHealBall",
      "en_US": [
        "Catching Pokémon is best accomplished\n",
        "by whittling the target’s HP down as\f",
        "low as possible, then tossing a Ball.\r",
        "But a Pokémon caught that way can’t\n",
        "be used in battle right away.\r",
        "That’s where the Heal Ball comes in\n",
        "handy.\r",
        "You can lower the target’s HP bar to\n",
        "red, put it to sleep, or paralyze it.\r",
        "The Heal Ball instantly heals whatever\n",
        "ails the Pokémon it catches!\r",
        "That’s the Pokémon-friendly Heal Ball!\n",
        "Please, do give it a try!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_ArticleQuickBall",
      "en_US": [
        "When attempting to catch a Pokémon,\n",
        "you want to cut the target’s HP.\r",
        "But a fleet-footed Pokémon could\n",
        "bolt if you take too much time.\r",
        "The Quick Ball is the solution to\n",
        "that dilemma.\r",
        "It’s designed to work best when\n",
        "thrown right at the start of battle!\r",
        "The Quick Ball: the perfect gift for\n",
        "the impatient Trainer!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SolaceonTownPokemonNewsPress_Text_ArticleDiveBall",
      "en_US": [
        "The Pokémon of the mothering sea\n",
        "aren’t like the others.\r",
        "If you are brave enough to face such\n",
        "intimidating Pokémon, the Dive Ball is\f",
        "perfect for you.\r",
        "For Pokémon you meet in the sea, and\n",
        "for Pokémon caught fishing...\r",
        "The Dive Ball is the Poké Ball you can\n",
        "count on!"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
